ExxonMobil Global Services Company is a subsidiary of Exxon Mobil Corporation that provides information technology, procurement and real estate management services to Exxon Mobil Corporation and its worldwide affiliates. ExxonMobil Global Services Company has certified to the Safe Harbor with respect to its collection of personal data from:
(1) employees located in the EEA or Switzerland for purposes which are necessary for the performance of the employment relationship and the operation of the business interests of Exxon Mobil Corporation or any of its affiliates;
(2) contractors located in the EEA or Switzerland for the purposes of administering the contractor and the operation of the business interests of Exxon Mobil Corporation or any of its affiliates;
(3) vendors and representatives of vendor companies located in the EEA or Switzerland for the purposes of managing the purchase and delivery of goods or services and the associated contractual relationship with Exxon Mobil Corporation or any of its affiliates;
(4) customers and representatives of customer companies located in the EEA or Switzerland for the purposes of managing the sale of goods or services and the associated contractual relationship with Exxon Mobil Corporation or any of its affiliates; and
(5) other third parties located in the EEA or Switzerland for the purposes of managing the relationship and interactions with Exxon Mobil Corporation or any of its affiliates.
